<li>New standard operational</li>
</ul>

<h3>Cost Recovery Timeline</h3>

<p>Most owners recover the digital lock investment within:</p>

<ul>
<li><strong>Meet-and-greet savings:</strong> 6-12 months</li>
<li><strong>Lost key elimination:</strong> Immediate (RM300-500/year saved)</li>
<li><strong>Review improvement:</strong> Higher ratings = more bookings = 10-15% income increase</li>
</ul>

<h2>Special Considerations for Melaka Properties</h2>

<h3>Humidity and Weather</h3>

<p>Melaka's tropical climate affects lock choice:</p>

<ul>
<li><strong>Indoor locks:</strong> Standard models work fine</li>
<li><strong>Outdoor-exposed locks:</strong> Need weather-resistant models</li>
<li><strong>Coastal properties:</strong> Corrosion-resistant models recommended</li>
</ul>

<h3>Power Outage Preparedness</h3>

<p>Digital locks need backup power:</p>

<ul>
<li><strong>Battery backup:</strong> 9-volt external battery compartment</li>
<li><strong>Physical key override:</strong> Emergency key for lockouts</li>
<li><strong>Low-battery alerts:</strong> Monitoring prevents failures</li>
</ul>

<h3>Building Management Regulations</h3>

<p>Some condos in Melaka restrict lock modifications:</p>

<ul>
<li><strong>Check with management:</strong> Before installing digital locks</li>
<li><strong>Approval may be needed:</strong> Submit lock specifications</li>
<li><strong>Strata title considerations:</strong> Some developments have specific rules</li>
</ul>

